波斯特·马龙表示，像泰勒·斯威夫特或碧昂丝一样出名“一定很糟糕” https://www.nme.com/news/music/post-malone-says-it-must-suck-to-be-as-known-as-taylor-swift-or-beyonce-3783395?utm_source=rss&utm_medium= rss&utm_campaign=后马龙说它必须像泰勒·斯威夫特或碧昂斯那样出名Liberty DunworthTue, 13 Aug 2024 16:04:02 +0000 Music NewsNewsCountryPopRap https://www.nme.com/?p=3783395 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Swift-Malone-Beyonce@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="泰勒·斯威夫特、波斯特·马龙和碧昂斯" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Swift-Malone-Beyonce@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Swift-Malone-Beyonce@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Swift-Malone-Beyonce@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Swift-Malone-Beyonce@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Swift-Malone-Beyonce@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Swift-Malone-Beyonce@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> “我什至无法想象自己能达到他们的水平”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/post-malone-says-it-must-suck-to-be-as-famous-as-taylor-swift-or-beyonce-3783395">波斯特·马龙 (Post Malone) 表示，像泰勒·斯威夫特 (Taylor Swift) 或碧昂丝 (Beyoncé) 那样出名“一定很糟糕”，</a>该帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Swift-Malone-Beyonce@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="泰勒·斯威夫特、波斯特·马龙和碧昂斯" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Swift-Malone-Beyonce@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Swift-Malone-Beyonce@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Swift-Malone-Beyonce@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Swift-Malone-Beyonce@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Swift-Malone-Beyonce@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Swift-Malone-Beyonce@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/post-malone">马龙（Post Malone）</a>曾说过，与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/taylor-swift">泰勒·斯威夫特（Taylor Swift）</a>或<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/beyonce">碧昂斯（Beyoncé）</a>具有相同的名声“必须吸引”。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多：<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/post-malone-austin-review-3474831">波斯特·马龙——《奥斯汀》评论：波斯蒂诚实地讲述了他的恶习</a></strong></li></ul><p>这位说唱歌手、歌手和词曲作者过去曾与两位流行歌星合作过，他在一次新的采访中透露，他不想获得与他们两人一样的名气。</p><p>这个话题是在对<a href="https://www.nytimes.com/2024/08/08/arts/music/post-malone-f-1-trillion-country-music.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《纽约时报》</em></a>的新采访中出现的，在那里他回顾了自己的时间与他们的2024年专辑发行。</p><p>他与斯威夫特合作制作了她的大专辑<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/taylor-swift-the-tortured-poets-department-lyrics-tracklist-3619454">《The Tortured Poets Department》</a> ，并与她一起演唱了歌曲<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/post-malone-and-florence-the-machine-to-feature-on-taylor-swifts-the-tortured-poets-department-3583153">《Fortnight》</a> 。他回忆说，在拍摄<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/taylor-swift-drops-video-for-post-malone-collaboration-fortnight-3689827">音乐视频</a>期间，歌手必须完全隐藏起来，才能在片场走动而不被狗仔队发现。</p><p> “我什至无法想象自己能达到他们的水平——这一定很糟糕，”波斯蒂（他的真名是奥斯汀·理查德·波斯特）告诉媒体。他补充说，斯威夫特需要“高尔夫球车上有一把雨伞和窗帘，这样无人机和直升机就无法拍摄到镜头”。</p><p> “压力太大了，”他补充道，并接着解释了当他在<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/miley-cyrus-and-post-malone-will-reportedly-feature-on-beyonces-cowboy-carter-3610753">合作曲目“LEVII&#39;S JEANS”</a>之前去与碧昂丝会面时，如何需要类似程度的安全保障。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="碧昂斯 &amp; Post Malone - LEVII&#39;S JEANS（官方歌词视频）" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/esnhbIbQHgM?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>在讨论他们在这首歌上的工作时间时，这位音乐家透露，他从未亲自见过贝伊，而是与贝伊团队的一名代表会面，并在两人通过短信讨论计划之前，贝伊将这首歌曲发送给了他在犹他州的住所。</p><p> “这太可怕了，”他说，并接着说，他感到“很荣幸能在这些人的附近。”</p><p>波斯蒂过去曾对两位艺人大加赞扬——既感谢碧昂斯让他出演<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/beyonce-cowboy-carter-album-review-tracklist-lyrics-3611699">《牛仔卡特》</a> ，又形容这张专辑“很美”，并告诉歌迷他对有机会与斯威夫特合作《牛仔卡特》感到“震惊”。 “TTPD”。</p><p> “像@taylorswift 这样的人一生中只有一次来到这个世界，”他在后者发布后不久写道。 “我对你的心和你的思想感到震惊，我非常荣幸能被要求在你的旅程中帮助你。我真的很爱你。谢谢泰伊。” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C5_yivCP1LP/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553